00:47:47.552 --> 00:47:48.910 align:middle line:90%


00:47:48.910 --> 00:47:52.930 align:middle line:84%
The burden of proof is now on
the side of the government.

00:47:52.930 --> 00:47:57.670 align:middle line:84%
Finally a great
scientist is recognizing

00:47:57.670 --> 00:48:00.520 align:middle line:90%
that this phenomenon is real.

00:48:00.520 --> 00:48:06.620 align:middle line:84%
Now the authorities hope to
demonstrate that this is not,

00:48:06.620 --> 00:48:09.410 align:middle line:84%
and that is going to be
very difficult, especially

00:48:09.410 --> 00:48:13.550 align:middle line:84%
with the kind of
proof we have now,

00:48:13.550 --> 00:48:17.940 align:middle line:84%
that it comes directly
from the authorities.

00:48:17.940 --> 00:48:20.670 align:middle line:84%
This is a new time,
a new beginning.

00:48:20.670 --> 00:48:25.670 align:middle line:84%
And I think Dr. Kaku set the
stage for the near future.

00:48:25.670 --> 00:48:28.970 align:middle line:84%
I hope you have
enjoyed this interview.

